data.description: Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom property in a highly sought-after neighborhood. This home offers numerous upgrades and features, making it a fantastic opportunity for your next home! Recent improvements include newer kitchen, newer main bathroom and newer roof. With hardwood floors, primary bedroom on the main floor, spacious deck in the backyard and a detached garage. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to own a beautifully home in a prime location!
